tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE instrument_usage_tracking (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
instrument_name VARCHAR(50),
usage_count INT,
last_used_date DATE,
user_id INT,
location VARCHAR(100))

CREATE TABLE usage_tracking (
    tracking_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    instrument_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    date DATE,
    duration_minutes INT
);

CREATE TABLE instrument_usage (
    user_id UUID,
    instrument_id UUID,
    usage_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    duration INT,
    PRIMARY KEY (user_id, instrument_id, usage_timestamp)
);
